{"lemma":"مُشْتَرَكٌ","slug":"مُشْتَرَكٌ","root":"ش.ر.ك","root_slug":"ش-ر-ك","root_link":"/words/roots/ش-ر-ك","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"مُشْتَرَكٌ","root":"شرك","pos":"N","occurrence_count":2},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["adj","noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":4},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n22237"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8F%D8%B4%D9%92%D8%AA%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%8E%D9%83%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"participant, subscriber"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"shared"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"common, mutual"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"joint"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Derived from the active participle of the verb اِشْتَرَكَ (ištaraka).\n\nDerived from the passive participle of اِشْتَرَكَ (ištaraka)."},"ipa":["/muʃ.ta.rik/","/muʃ.ta.rak/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n22237","headword_ar":"مُشْتَرَكٌ","root":"$rk","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", applied to a road ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tariyq","text_ar":"طَرِيق"},{"kind":"text","text":", Mgh, Msb, TA), is for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mu$otarakN fiyhi","text_ar":"مُشْتَرَكٌ فِيهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) meaning ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Shared in:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in which the people are equal"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sharers"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b2-  Hence,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^ajiyru Almu$otaraku","text_ar":"الاَجِيرُ المُشْتَرَكُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in my copy of the Mgh, erroneously,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Almu$otariku","text_ar":"المُشْتَرِكُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The hired man"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is shared in;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whose work no one has for himself exclusively of others, but who works for every one who repairs to him for work, like the tailor in the sitting-places of the markets;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who works for whom he pleases:"},{"kind":"text","text":"as to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajiyru Almu$otaraki","text_ar":"اَجِيرُ المُشْتَرَكِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", it is not right, unless the word thus governed in the gen. case be expl. as an inf. n. (Mgh.) ―         -b3-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlfariyDapu Almu$ar~akapu","text_ar":"الفَرِيضَةُ المُشَرَّكَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", above. ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AisomN mu$otarakN","text_ar":"اِسْمٌ مُشْتَرَكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in like manner for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mu$otarakN fiyhi","text_ar":"مُشْتَرَكٌ فِيهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A noun shared in"},{"kind":"text","text":"by several meanings; i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a homonym;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a noun shared in by many meanings, such as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EayonN","text_ar":"عَيْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mz, 25th"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nwE","text_ar":"نوع"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and TA in the present art. and in the Intr.:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mu$otarakN","text_ar":"مُشْتَرَكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies a word"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having two,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"more, meanings;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and is applied to a noun, and to the pret. of a verb as denoting predication and prayer, and to the aor. as denoting the present and the future, and to a particle: (Mz ubi suprà:) ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mu$otarakN","text_ar":"مُشْتَرَكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"used as a subst., meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a homonym,"},{"kind":"text","text":"has for its pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mu$otarakaAtN","text_ar":"مُشْتَرَكَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b5-  ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHis~u Almu$otaraku","text_ar":"الحِسُّ المُشْتَرَكُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Almu$otaraku fiyhi","text_ar":"المُشْتَرَكُ فِيهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", signifies, in the conventional language of the philosophers,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The faculty of fancy;"},{"kind":"text","text":"so called because “ participated in ” by the five senses: but it is vulgarly used as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"common sense."},{"kind":"text","text":"] ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mu$otarakN","text_ar":"مُشْتَرَكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied to a man, [for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mu$otarakN fiyhi","text_ar":"مُشْتَرَكٌ فِيهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Talking to himself, like him who is affected with anxiety;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, S, K, TA; [in the CK, erroneously,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mu$orikN","text_ar":"مُشْرِكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":";])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his judgment being shared in; not one."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Msb"]}]},"classical_definitions":{"source":"hawramani","url":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/%D9%85%D8%B4%D8%AA%D8%B1%D9%83/","headword_ar":"مشترك","entries":[{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_18","lexicon_en":"Al-Sharīf al-Jurjānī, Kitāb al-Taʿrīfāt (d. 1413 CE)","lexicon_ar":"كتاب التعريفات للشريف الجرجاني","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=23661#831315","body_html":"<span>المشترك: ما وضع لمعنى كثير بوضع كثير، كالعين؛ لاشتراكه بين المعاني، ومعنى الكثرة ما يقابل القلة، فيدخل فيه المشترك بين المعنيين فقط، كالقرء، والشفق، فيكون مشتركًا بالنسبة إلى الجميع، ومجملًا بالنسبة إلى كل واحد والاشتراك بين الشيئين، إن كان بالنوع يسمى: مماثلة، كاشتراك زيد وعمرو في الإنسانية، وإن كان بالجنس، يسمى: مجانسة، كاشتراك إنسان وفرس في الحيوانية، وإن كان بالعرض، إن كان في الكم يسمى: مادة، كاشتراك ذراع من خشب وذراع من ثوب، في الطول، وإن كان في الكيف، يسمى: مشابهة، كاشتراك الإنسان والحجر في السواد، وإن كان بالمضاف، يسمى: مناسبة، كاشتراك زيد وعمرو في بنوة بكر، وإن كان بالشكل، يسمى: مشاكلة، كاشتراك الأرض والهواء في الكرية، وإن كان بالوضع المخصوص، يسمى: موازنة، وهو ألا يختلف البعد بينهما، كسطح كل فلك، وإن كان بالأطراف، يسمى: مطابقة، كاشتراك الإجانتين في الأطراف.</span>"}]}}